prompt: A serene minimalist workspace featuring a light oak desk, a high-resolution monitor displaying a clean code interface, and a small succulent plant. Soft, diffused lighting from an overhead skylight. Predominantly light beige and cream tones with subtle wood textures. Focus on clean lines and a sense of focused calm. High-resolution, professional quality. Medium shot, shallow depth of field to gently blur the background.
revised_prompt: Generate a serene minimalist workspace image, depicted with predominantly light beige and cream tones that highlight subtle wood textures. The space should contain a light oak desk, and on it, a high-resolution monitor displaying a clean code interface, accompanied by a small succulent plant. Soft, diffused lighting should pour from an overhead skylight, casting a peaceful ambiance. The image should convey a sense of focused calm, with clean lines and an organized aesthetic. The image should be of high-resolution, professional quality. Set it to be a medium shot, with a shallow depth of field used to subtly blur the background.
